  <h3 id="application_server_security_information">Application server security information</h3> 
  <p></p> 
  <p>When securing your application server, carefully consider implementing the measures described by your server vendor, including the following:</p> 
  <ul> 
   <li><p>Using non-obvious administrator user name</p></li> 
   <li><p>Disabling unnecessary services</p></li> 
   <li><p>Securing the console manager</p></li> 
   <li><p>Enabling secure cookies</p></li> 
   <li><p>Closing unneeded ports</p></li> 
   <li><p>Limiting clients by IP addresses or domains</p></li> 
   <li><p>Using the Java™ Security Manager to programmatically restrict privileges </p></li> 
  </ul> 
