  <h3 id="database_security_information">Database security information</h3> 
  <p></p> 
  <p>When securing your database, consider implementing the measures described by your database vendor, including the following:</p> 
  <ul> 
   <li><p>Restricting operations with access control lists (ACLs)</p></li> 
   <li><p>Using non-standard ports</p></li> 
   <li><p>Hiding the database behind a firewall</p></li> 
   <li><p>Encrypting sensitive data before writing it to the database (see the database manufacturer’s documentation)</p></li> 
